   | STATIC | STRING | CPVIRTUAL | ENUM | CPTYPEDEF | TYPEQUAL | BUILTIN
   | CPFRIEND | CPOPERATOR | TEMPLATE | CPTHROW | TYPENAME_KEYWORD | USING 
